Feature: Extract var

  Scenario: Extracting region
    When I insert "abc(1 + 2 + 3, 4 + 5);"
    And I turn on js2-mode
    And I turn on js2-refactor-mode
    And I go to the front of the word "1"
    And I set the mark
    And I go to the end of the word "2"
    And I press "C-c C-m ev"
    And I press "C-u DEL"
    And I type "three"
    Then I should see:
    """
    var three = 1 + 2;
    abc(three + 3, 4 + 5);
    """

